<div class="container">
<h2>A Lasting Gift for the Smithsonian National Museum of Natural History</h2>
<p>Link your legacy with the Museum. A gift in your will or estate plan ensures that we can continue to inspire curiosity about the natural world through our unparalleled research, collections, exhibitions, and education outreach programs well into the future.</p>
<p>Become a valued member of the Museum&rsquo;s family with a gift in your estate.</p>
<p><a href="/nmnh/legacy-society" class="stlButton" style="width: auto;">Learn about our Legacy&nbsp;Society &raquo;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
