                <div id="stl-getting-started-container">
                    <div class="container">
                        <h2>Planned Gifts</h2>
<p>Inspire future Museum visitors with a gift that extends beyond your lifetime.</p>
<h3>Wills and Living Trusts</h3>
<p>You can ensure your support for the Natural History Museum continues on by including a <a href="/nmnh/gift-in-your-will-or-living-trust">gift in your will</a> or living trust.</p>
<h3>Beneficiary Designations</h3>
<p>Find increased flexibility in your giving by naming the Smithsonian National Museum of Natural History <a href="/nmnh/beneficiary-designations">as a beneficiary</a> in your estate plan.</p>
<h3>Charitable Gift Annuities</h3>
<p>There's a way for you to support the Museum and feel confident that you have dependable income in your retirement years. You can do this with a charitable gift annuity.</p>
<p>This type of donation can provide you with regular payments and allow us to further our work. You can also qualify for a variety of tax benefits, including a federal income tax charitable deduction when you itemize.</p>
<h3>Additional Gifts</h3>
<p>There are many other types of planned gifts that may fit your long-term goals and help secure the future for you and your family, as well as the Museum. To learn more, please contact Virginia Kromm, Associate Director for Advancement, at <a href="mailto:NMNH-Advancement@si.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="s.linkTrackVars='events,eVar21'; s.linkTrackEvents='event11'; s.events='event11';s.eVar21='NMNH Homepage: Additional gifts email link'; s.tl(this,'o','Site Tool');">NMNH-Advancement@si.edu</a>.</p>
<div class="feature-callout">
<div class="bequest-language">
<h3>Sample Language for Your Will</h3>
<p>I give [____% of the residue of my estate], or [the sum of ________ dollars] to the Smithsonian National Museum of Natural History in Washington, D.C., for its general purposes [or program].</p>
<p>Tax ID: #53-0206027</p>
</div>
<div class="contact-info">
<div class="contact-inner-wrap">
<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>We would be happy to illustrate how your gift makes an impact at the Museum. Simply contact Virginia Kromm, Associate Director for Advancement, at 202&#45;633&#45;0821 or <a href="#" class="contactEMAddr" data-uname="NMNH-Advancement" data-domain="si.edu" >NMNH-Advancement@si.edu</a>.</p>
</div>
